{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0df4c2fc-32cc-44a0-a07d-81eccace0949","content":"Good news — with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` **natively uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform**. You **no longer need** `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`. That property was a .NET 9-era opt-in bridge; .NET 10 makes it the default.\n\nYour project just needs this cleanup — remove the now-unnecessary property:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Me9nkZAokJcU93rg4C6SkW","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01WyUUekCvPPp4McEtyYX3ZE","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-0369e7ed4f0c46fd9f13939201f3184e/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-0369e7ed4f0c46fd9f13939201f3184e/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"0fc14eca-1f31-440b-9203-3775d8a17041","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about native MTP support.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) without needing the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property. Starting with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` uses MTP by default when the test project is an MTP-based project (i.e., it has `EnableMSTestRunner` or similar runner enabled).\n\nSo the answer is:\n1. In .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively integrates with MTP — you no longer need `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>`.\n\n\n2. They should remove that property since it's now redundant with .NET 10 SDK.\n3. `EnableMSTestRunner` is still required to configure the test project to use MTP in the first place.\n\nThis aligns with Microsoft's announcement for .NET 10 Preview, where `dotnet test` gained native MTP support, making the bridge property from .NET 9 unnecessary.","outputTokens":654},"id":"fb7475a8-2dff-4e2a-bf34-f9c655e67c35","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:55:50.850Z","parentId":"709526a2-bae8-4bba-b098-0558461260b5"}
